Class 5: Design Patterns

MVC - Model View Controller
	
	Pluses:
		Standard
		Tested
		Solves common problems
	
	Model (Testable) -- state of world
		Data
		Loc
		Vel
		Dir
		 
	View (Testable by Google's huge AI team) -- view of the world
		where the orc is displayed
		Draws the orc based on model's (overall) data
		Where mice, keyboards, buttons, etc are created
	
	Controller
		tick()
		listeners
		
	